Holdsport Raises $136 Million Before Listing on Johannesburg Stock Market

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-13T06:04:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/holdsport-raises-136-million-before-listing-on-johannesburg-stock-market.html
Holdsport Ltd. said its existing
shareholders placed stock in the company at 31 rand each for a
total value of 930 million rand. The company will list its
securities on the  Johannesburg Stock Exchange  on July 18.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  